","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"dzfE4hj9qG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震学工作者在全球范围布设了许多地震仪，有的布设在地表，有的布设在地下。\n有的地震仪配备了充电设备（如太阳能面板）、网络通讯设备，以便长期稳定地运行，并实时传输数据。","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"TEPQ0DY48c"}],"key":"G70Qjw7xyA"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震发生后，其激发的地震波会在地球内部传播。地震波传播至地震仪位置时，地震仪会随即将其记录下来，\n并将其转换为数字记录，存储起来。配有蜂窝电话、宽带网络或卫星通信系统的台站，还可以将数据实时\n传输到数据处理中心。最后，科研人员和大众可以利用互联网在数据中心下载数据，开展研究工作。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"ROq2pyMEEK"}],"key":"hzT6Wyhscr"},{"type":"container","kind":"figure","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/seismology101/build/data-transimission-355c0c3f6cea7c0fac65d274d1f3a829.jpg","alt":"地震数据记录和传输示意图","width":"95%","align":"center","key":"Dmg9usn1VK","urlSource":"data-transimission.jpg"},{"type":"caption","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震学数据地记录和传输示意图。引自\n","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"zaMjnMSWjG"},{"type":"link","url":"http://www.usarray.org/public/about/how#anchor1","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How does a seismic station work?","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"p2d99Fc70y"}],"urlSource":"http://www.usarray.org/public/about/how#anchor1","key":"sa4ooOTWv5"}],"key":"HoaiidNuZi"}],"key":"QGyS624qBQ"}],"enumerator":"1","key":"M9qiylbxQn"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"仪器响应","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"CRjTjg9